    {
        "url": "/quotes/pamela_meyer_825046",
        "quote": "A good lie detector doesn't jump to conclusions but tries to understand the person across the table, her personality, and her motivations. Your goal as a lie spotter isn't to point the finger and say, 'You're lying' - your goal is to get to the truth.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Pamela Meyer",
            "url": "/quotes/pamela_meyer_825046"
