    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/pamela_meyer_825069",
        "quote": "Pummeling an answer out of someone never works. You cannot intimidate someone with aggressive language and think they'll be more forthcoming... that's a caricature of interrogation, part of the TV culture of what it looks like.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Pamela Meyer",
            "url": "/quotes/pamela_meyer_825069"
