    {
        "url": "/quotes/pamela_meyer_825052",
        "quote": "A narcissist like Trump must constantly inflate and exaggerate in order to keep the supply trains running. He has to brag about how, 'I have a very high IQ' or concoct stories about people agreeing with him.",
